ke for even the most computer-literacy-challenged client to update.\nI\'ve tried a few shiny new plugins and always come back to this one. It just works.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Absolutely perfect.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 von 5 Sternen\" data-title-template=\"%s von 5 Sternen\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Von <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/milan574\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3a23fe3fc74c9d8491b2846b199a52f2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3a23fe3fc74c9d8491b2846b199a52f2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/milan574\" class=\"reviewer-name\">milan574</a> am <span class=\"review-date\">January 9, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Absolutely perfect. It has everything you need for a community site. I give 6 stars.\nthx</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">This is a must-have plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 von 5 Sternen\" data-title-template=\"%s von 5 Sternen\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\